lead_paragraph: Atlantic City's crumbling casino market disintegrated even further Saturday as the owners of the Trump Plaza casino said they expect to shut down in mid-September.

headline.main: Owners of Trump Plaza Casino Expect It Will Close
headline.print_headline: Owners of Trump Plaza Casino Expect It Will Close
